MATTHEW HENDERSHOT:
Unfortunately, we're

00:54:46.440 --> 00:54:48.260
out of time, or we'd
take a couple more.

00:54:48.260 --> 00:54:51.444
If you guys do want to see the
full episodes of the shows,

00:54:51.444 --> 00:54:52.860
and everything
we've done out, you

00:54:52.860 --> 00:54:56.520
can go to songcraftpresents.com,
or go straight to the source,

00:54:56.520 --> 00:54:59.264
and go to YouTube.com
slash songcraftpresents.

00:54:59.264 --> 00:55:01.180
Thank you guys for taking
the time to join me.

00:55:01.180 --> 00:55:02.110
Thank you as an audience.

00:55:02.110 --> 00:55:02.790
ROB REINHART: Thank you.

00:55:02.790 --> 00:55:03.410
MICHAEL CREHORE:
Thanks, Matthew.

